---
import { SITE_DISCLAIMER } from "../consts";
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>关于本站 - 398的美股策略｜美股科技投研</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Arial, "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
        background: #f6f8fb;
        color: #1f2937;
      }

      main {
        max-width: 860px;
        margin: 60px auto;
        padding: 0 24px;
        line-height: 1.9;
      }

      a {
        color: #2563eb;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      .box {
        background: white;
        padding: 36px;
        border-radius: 18px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 34px;
      }

      p {
        color: #4b5563;
      }

      .warning {
        background: #eef2ff;
        border-left: 5px solid #2563eb;
        padding: 18px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        color: #475569;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <p><a href="/">← 返回首页</a></p>

      <div class="box">
        <h1>关于本站</h1>

        <p>
          “398的美股策略｜美股科技投研”用于整理美股科技公司研究、行业主题观察、策略历史复盘和财报跟踪。本站面向中文读者，重点放在研究框架和风险意识，不写过度个人化介绍。
        </p>

        <div class="warning">
          {SITE_DISCLAIMER}
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
